
Help on: newbie

The help system is accessible via the 'help' command.
To see a list of help topics, type 'help topics'.

This game has mostly been tested with TinyFugue and
ZMud mud-clients. If you are playing with telnet you
might want to 'set idleprompt off'.
(see also: 'help settings')

Use 'map legend' to see what the letters in the city 
map mean.

Use 'map large' to see a larger map.

To request help use the newbie channel.

See also: channels
          combat
          movement
          food
          experience
